# Auth

- Use **Better Auth** only: `auth` from `@/lib/auth`, client via `@/lib/auth-client`, HTTP handler at `app/api/auth/[...all]`.
- Keep **`BETTER_AUTH_SECRET`**, **`BETTER_AUTH_URL`**, and **`NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL`** aligned per environment (local vs Netlify). Mismatched origins break cookies and redirects.
- Do not store passwords in custom tables; use Better Auth’s `user` / `account` models.
